text: Mundamia is a suburb in the City of Shoalhaven in South Coast in New South Wales in Australia. It is about 5 km west of Nowra by road.https://dcp2014.shoalhaven.nsw.gov.au/sites/default/files/DCP2014AmendmentNo5_ChapterNB1_MundamiaUrbanReleaseArea.pdf In 2016, 70 people lived there. University of Wollongong's Shoalhaven campus is built there. == References == Category:Settlements in New South Wales
title: Mundamia
